com.facebook.rendercore.extensions

Class MountExtension<Input,State>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.rendercore.extensions.MountExtension<Input,State>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DynamicPropsExtension, EndToEndTestingExtension, IncrementalMountExtension, LithoViewAttributesExtension, TransitionsExtension, VisibilityMountExtension

    public abstract class MountExtension<Input,State>
extends java.lang.Object
    Mount extension which can be registered by a MountState as an extension which can override mounting behaviour. MountState will rely on the extensions registered on the MountDelegate to decide what to mount or unmount. If no extensions are registered on the MountState's delegate, it falls back to its default behaviour.
